Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:06.24,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}watashi ga umareta asa no machi yuki no naka ni umoreta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:11.78,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sore wa sore wa chiisai te de aozora wo aoida
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:18.41,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sanagara mukashi kara yoku shiru tonari no ano ko no you ni
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:23.27,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}katahou no mimitabu de kiku sotsugyou no canon
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:29.23,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}hitori demo daijoubu yo tte mekureteru watashi no story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:31.51,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}dareka no sei ni shitai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:35.70,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tsurai naa iya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:41.05,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kanashikutte naite bakkari itara me ga tokete nakunatta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:46.47,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}aki ni nari mata fuyu ni nari hitotsu toshi wo totta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:53.26,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tooku made nigete iru tsumori demo owaranai kimi no story
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:55.52,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}niya niya waratte iru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.11,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}fugainaiya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:05.25,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}sugari nagara oikakete mitemo ashige ni saretemo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.44,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}aita ana wo fusagou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:10.36,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}chigai nai ya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:17.74,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}fugainai ya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:28.36,cloveroprom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}tsurai naa iya iya
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:06.24,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}My hometown lay buried in snow the morning I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.07,0:00:11.78,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I looked up at the blue sky with my tiny hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:18.41,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}The face of the girl next door that I've known so well...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:23.27,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's as familiar as the graduation canon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:29.23,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Thriving in solitude has been mistaken as my life story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:31.51,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I want to blame it on someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.51,0:00:35.70,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. No, I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:41.05,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Tears and sorrow caused me to miss my chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.67,0:00:46.47,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Autumn passed, winter came again, and I became a year older.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:53.26,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}You think you've run far away, but your story never ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:55.52,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}And yet, you're smirking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.11,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:01:05.25,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Even if I have to cling to you, chase after you, and get kicked down...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:07.44,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...I'll close the hole that's opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:10.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}...without a doubt. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.36,0:01:17.74,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so cowardly. No...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:28.36,cloveropeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}It's so difficult. I hate it. I hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:51.32,clover,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Hagu?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.09,0:01:55.48,clover,,0,0,0,,Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:02:00.72,clover,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Hagu? Your hiccups won't stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:02.41,clover,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.95,0:02:04.61,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll show you how to make them stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:06.55,clover,,0,0,0,,Do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.55,0:02:09.96,clover,,0,0,0,,...and drink from the other side of the cup, then they'll stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.33,0:02:15.22,clover,,0,0,0,,This is a special technique that I learned from my best friend in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.22,0:02:17.34,clover,,0,0,0,,T-That's creepy, Shuu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:19.09,clover,,0,0,0,,Now, give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:24.47,clover,,0,0,0,,No, you need to stretch your neck more, and put your mouth on the opposite side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:27.38,clover,,0,0,0,,Right, like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:31.42,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, man... You spilled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:38.29,clover,,0,0,0,,The problem with this technique is its difficulty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:42.32,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, now that I think about it, Rika used to spill all the time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:51.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Shoot, hold on for a bit, Hagu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.17,0:02:52.33,clover,,0,0,0,,I'll go get you another cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.28,clover,,0,0,0,,We'll give it another try.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:01.59,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.96,0:03:03.54,clover,,0,0,0,,You have the hiccups?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:05.55,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:09.44,clover,,0,0,0,,I hear that you'll die if you hiccup a hundred times in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:10.08,clover,,0,0,0,,What'll you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:14.02,clover,,0,0,0,,100!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:17.03,clover,,0,0,0,,T-There's no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:18.95,clover,,0,0,0,,99!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.95,0:03:20.66,clover,,0,0,0,,...you can die from that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:22.44,clover,,0,0,0,,98!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:25.96,clover,,0,0,0,,97!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:29.12,clover,,0,0,0,,Uh oh, you only have 96 more left to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:33.08,clover,,0,0,0,,96!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:37.29,clover,,0,0,0,,Here, Hagu. Give it another try!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:38.33,clover,,0,0,0,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:39.63,clover,,0,0,0,,She's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.10,0:03:42.21,clover,,0,0,0,,61!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:43.25,clover,,0,0,0,,60!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:44.30,clover,,0,0,0,,59!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.39,clover,,0,0,0,,This should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:52.89,clover,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.31,clover,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:54.75,clover,,0,0,0,,50!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.14,0:03:56.97,clover,,0,0,0,,49!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.97,0:03:58.31,clover,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.31,0:03:59.31,clover,,0,0,0,,48!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:02.82,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, you're hiccuping too fast! Oh, well! 47!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:03.73,clover,,0,0,0,,46!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:04.57,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.73,0:04:06.76,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh no! You only have 45 more left to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:07.67,clover,,0,0,0,,Morita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:08.20,clover,,0,0,0,,T-Takemoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:17.12,clover,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:19.58,clover,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.58,0:04:20.35,clover,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:27.06,clover,,0,0,0,,Takemoto-kun... the h-hiccups...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:31.83,clover,,0,0,0,,He said that I'll die if I hiccuped a hundred times in a row...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:34.93,clover,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, Morita-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:38.17,clover,,0,0,0,,Here, Hagu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.04,0:04:43.31,clover,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:48.52,clover,,0,0,0,,Here, try drinking from each side...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.00,0:04:51.15,clover,,0,0,0,,...while holding the chopsticks in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:04:59.24,clover,,0,0,0,,That's right. Don't rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:01.38,clover,,0,0,0,,Slowly, slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:03.65,clover,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.14,0:05:07.46,clover,,0,0,0,,They stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:09.42,clover,,0,0,0,,They stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:10.55,clover,,0,0,0,,It works, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:12.68,clover,,0,0,0,,I learned it from my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.68,0:05:14.50,clover,,0,0,0,,This will make them stop most of the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:22.83,clover,,0,0,0,,T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:26.18,clover,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.33,0:05:41.94,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kimi ni aeta natsugumo ni natta\NI became a summer spider and met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:49.75,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}nekorogatte kurukuru ni karamatte fuzaketa\NLying around, we wrapped around each other on the web...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:49.01,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Hagu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:56.81,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kaze no you ni sukoshi dake yurenagara\N...wavering slightly in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:52.38,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.39,0:05:59.27,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Since then, Hagu-chan started avoiding me for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.81,0:06:02.55,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}machi no sumi no dobugawa ni atta\NI floated down the drainage ditch at the edge of town...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:10.14,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kowaresou na sasabune ni notte nagareta\N...on a rickety bamboo leaf boat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.46,0:06:09.53,thoughts,,0,0,0,,The words had just slipped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:18.59,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kiri no you ni kasuka ni kienagara\N...slowly fading away like the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:14.08,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Although I knew what her answer would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.85,0:06:19.54,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Maybe I shouldn't have said it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.74,0:06:30.99,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}hitori wo wasureta sekai ni mizushibuki haneagete\NSplashing water on a world that's forgotten about loneliness...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:23.74,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But I don't regret it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.54,0:06:33.20,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I always thought that I'd regret it if I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:42.31,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}bata ashi ooki na sugata ga oyogidasu\N...kicking through the water, a large shape begins to swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:35.37,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.90,0:06:39.85,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I look up at the sky and it's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:41.72,thoughts,,0,0,0,,So beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:48.47,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kimi ni aeta natsugumo ni natta\NI became a summer spider and met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:56.12,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}nekorogatte kurukuru ni karamatte fuzaketa\NLying around, we wrapped around each other on the web...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:07:05.44,cloverinsert,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}kaze no you ni sukoshi dake yurenagara\N...wavering slightly in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:19.33,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:22.10,clover,,0,0,0,,This unrefined design...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:27.26,clover,,0,0,0,,And this overwhelming presence that nonetheless complements the plant's expression!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:29.76,clover,,0,0,0,,And to top it off, it's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.76,0:07:31.24,clover,,0,0,0,,It's great. Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.24,0:07:33.32,clover,,0,0,0,,T-Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:35.24,clover,,0,0,0,,We're glad to hear you like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:40.85,clover,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it was a little too big?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:42.42,clover,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:44.30,clover,,0,0,0,,He was quite pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:48.53,clover,,0,0,0,,He's usually a difficult person to deal with, but he talked with us for such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:51.28,clover,,0,0,0,,I was pleased as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:54.10,clover,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to the vase that you made, Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:55.10,clover,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:58.75,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I don't deserve the praise, Rika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:00.50,clover,,0,0,0,,Please go ahead and eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:01.81,clover,,0,0,0,,Sure, thanks for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.89,0:08:14.82,thoughts,,0,0,0,,I wonder what she looks like through Mayama's eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:22.77,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Does he look at her with an aching heart, longing to touch her shoulder and her pale cheeks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:30.05,thoughts,,0,0,0,,What sound does his heart make when it strains?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.58,0:08:35.58,thoughts,,0,0,0,,What emotions does he hold in while he's at that office?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:39.18,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Always alone with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:44.31,clover,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the good work, and welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:47.64,clover,,0,0,0,,Here are some towels and paper towels.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:51.83,clover,,0,0,0,,Please roll up the paper towels and put them in your shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:54.87,clover,,0,0,0,,And here's some hot tea for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:56.72,clover,,0,0,0,,Yay, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.73,0:09:03.13,clover,,0,0,0,,You're so maternal, Mayama.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:06.84,clover,,0,0,0,,Huh? Something tells me I shouldn't be too thrilled to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:11.19,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, and Rika-san, once youre done drinking, please go to your bedroom and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:11.90,clover,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:17.65,clover,,0,0,0,,We're waiting for Mori-san's check, but it'll probably be after 11 o'clock before he contacts us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:20.29,clover,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.29,0:09:21.97,clover,,0,0,0,,Please get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:23.97,clover,,0,0,0,,You didn't sleep last night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:25.83,clover,,0,0,0,,I got plenty of rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:30.52,clover,,0,0,0,,You were drawing blueprints in your room until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:33.85,clover,,0,0,0,,I could hear your computer chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:38.51,thoughts,,0,0,0,,And Mayama was listening below Rika-san's room the entire time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:43.47,clover,,0,0,0,,Based on past patterns, it'll be close to midnight before Mori-san sends us the data.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:46.06,clover,,0,0,0,,Please get some rest instead of waiting around while doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:48.94,clover,,0,0,0,,If there are any pressing matters, I'll call your cell phone to wake you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:50.69,clover,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:53.31,clover,,0,0,0,,Then I guess I'll get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:55.92,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Yamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:59.15,clover,,0,0,0,,Our next appointment is on Wednesday, but we have some things to take care of before then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:04.52,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yamada and I will make that file, so please don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:08.64,clover,,0,0,0,,Well then, goodnight, Rika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:10.31,clover,,0,0,0,,Yes, goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:15.70,clover,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:19.74,clover,,0,0,0,,Before we get to work, why don't we order dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.23,0:10:21.92,clover,,0,0,0,,What do you want, Yamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.92,0:10:24.73,clover,,0,0,0,,Soba, Chinese, or pizza?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:26.95,clover,,0,0,0,,Pizza!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:32.32,clover,,0,0,0,,Yes, a triple L magnum deluxe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.32,0:10:33.61,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:34.96,clover,,0,0,0,,Say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:38.96,clover,,0,0,0,,What do you usually talk about, Mayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.67,0:10:40.67,clover,,0,0,0,,With Rika-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.78,0:10:42.99,clover,,0,0,0,,What do we talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:44.97,clover,,0,0,0,,We talk about...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:47.86,clover,,0,0,0,,Usually something like...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:50.03,clover,,0,0,0,,"I wonder if it'll be sunny tomorrow?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:53.04,clover,,0,0,0,,Or, "Do you think the typhoon will come our way?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:58.09,clover,,0,0,0,,Or, "What model should we choose for our new laptop?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.09,0:11:00.12,clover,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:05.16,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, when I think about it, it seems like we only talk about work and the weather, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:09.49,clover,,0,0,0,,But she doesn't talk that much, to begin with...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:13.71,clover,,0,0,0,,But haven't you been working together for four years already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.89,0:11:16.46,clover,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.89,0:11:21.11,clover,,0,0,0,,Is it strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.42,0:11:25.57,clover,,0,0,0,,Is it strange that we don't really talk about anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:27.29,clover,,0,0,0,,No, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.43,clover,,0,0,0,,It's not really strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:34.09,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:37.57,clover,,0,0,0,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:39.87,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:44.23,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:15.89,clover,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:17.30,clover,,0,0,0,,Kaoru...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:18.61,clover,,0,0,0,,How's work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:25.48,clover,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:32.25,clover,,0,0,0,,There's a lot of people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.00,0:12:34.52,clover,,0,0,0,,It is a school, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:41.17,clover,,0,0,0,,So everyone here is trying to become an artist or find other creative jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:44.69,clover,,0,0,0,,I don't think there's that much demand for them out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:50.09,clover,,0,0,0,,People like our father are rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:52.95,clover,,0,0,0,,People with talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.18,0:12:56.12,clover,,0,0,0,,You must think that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:13:00.41,clover,,0,0,0,,No, you understand because it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:04.87,clover,,0,0,0,,Did something bad happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:07.69,clover,,0,0,0,,No, things are going smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:12.39,clover,,0,0,0,,In terms of funds, we're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:16.47,clover,,0,0,0,,But I want to push through in one go, Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:25.90,clover,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:28.33,clover,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:31.09,clover,,0,0,0,,I know, Kaoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:35.31,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:39.83,clover,,0,0,0,,What did you used to talk about with Rika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:41.64,clover,,0,0,0,,Huh, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:43.19,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:46.57,clover,,0,0,0,,You've been going to Rika's to help out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:48.79,clover,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:53.81,clover,,0,0,0,,Back when we were students, I was always talking to Rika about the books that I read.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:13:58.19,clover,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was the only one talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:02.88,clover,,0,0,0,,Biographies of artists, historical background of an art piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:05.75,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, and about anatomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:11.19,clover,,0,0,0,,Whenever we were alone, Rika would say, "Please tell me about something."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.19,0:14:13.86,clover,,0,0,0,,It was hard for me to always have something to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.86,0:14:20.14,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, I did like books, so I was actually happy to have someone to talk about them with.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:25.34,clover,,0,0,0,,I'd be in the library every day going through art textbooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:29.71,clover,,0,0,0,,There was even a time when a professor mistook me as being studious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.07,0:14:34.86,clover,,0,0,0,,Wonderful! Hanamoto-kun, you are a model student of the arts!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.86,0:14:38.60,clover,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who seriously studies art history!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:38.99,clover,,0,0,0,,Sensei, I'm in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:43.97,clover,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm here thanks to things like that though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:47.19,clover,,0,0,0,,By the way, why are you asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:52.35,clover,,0,0,0,,Um, well, whenever I'm alone with Rika-san, things get quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.84,clover,,0,0,0,,I was wondering what I could do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:56.50,clover,,0,0,0,,You don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:15:00.42,clover,,0,0,0,,The more she gets used to you, the less she speaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.65,0:15:04.60,clover,,0,0,0,,When she was with Harada, she almost never spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:09.62,clover,,0,0,0,,They got along very well, but they were always just hanging out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.27,0:15:15.55,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika, you see, speaks less when she's with someone she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:22.78,thoughts,,0,0,0,,She speaks less when she's with someone she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:31.93,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Is it strange that we don't really talk about anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.89,0:15:38.06,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.75,0:15:39.75,clover,,0,0,0,,You idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.61,0:15:44.47,clover,,0,0,0,,Two pieces of "1A" and two pieces of "5C".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:48.37,clover,,0,0,0,,They'd like those pieces for their store in Kamakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.94,0:15:51.05,clover,,0,0,0,,We'll take a look at the store next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:52.98,clover,,0,0,0,,That's amazing, Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:56.24,clover,,0,0,0,,You might be able to quit your school job and make a living doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:57.04,clover,,0,0,0,,Truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:16:01.06,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, not at all. I'm still using the school's kiln, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:05.04,clover,,0,0,0,,Now then, we'll need a file for the pieces and a mold...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.74,0:16:07.16,clover,,0,0,0,,...by tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:10.62,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.80,0:16:19.38,clover,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with Rika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:22.34,clover,,0,0,0,,She's not coming back from the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.85,0:16:24.76,clover,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's not feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.24,0:16:30.69,clover,,0,0,0,,Hiccups?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.69,0:16:32.72,clover,,0,0,0,,Let's leave her be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:33.77,clover,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:36.77,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Listen, Rika.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:39.83,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Drink the water from the opposite end of the cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:41.23,thoughts,,0,0,0,,They'll stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.47,0:16:51.99,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika-san's hiccups aren't stopping...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:53.66,clover,,0,0,0,,What should we do about food?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.96,0:16:55.77,clover,,0,0,0,,The stores will close soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.34,0:17:02.50,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.88,clover,,0,0,0,,Rika-san, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:10.90,clover,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:12.73,clover,,0,0,0,,Your shirt is wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:15.92,clover,,0,0,0,,I spilled a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:47.97,clover,,0,0,0,,Here, please drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.23,0:17:49.73,clover,,0,0,0,,Sugar water?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:52.14,clover,,0,0,0,,We used to do this back home to stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.93,0:17:57.23,clover,,0,0,0,,Please take my word for it and give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.45,clover,,0,0,0,,See? It stopped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:16.76,clover,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:19.39,thoughts,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:20.87,thoughts,,0,0,0,,It stopped, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.64,0:18:23.64,clover,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:27.55,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.28,0:18:29.79,clover,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Mayama-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:34.80,clover,,0,0,0,,So you're going to Rika-san's, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.16,0:18:38.77,clover,,0,0,0,,You're so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:40.40,clover,,0,0,0,,You'll cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:47.65,clover,,0,0,0,,You're going out of your way to burn the sight of them together into your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:54.31,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But you should go, if that's what you need to do to get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:59.37,thoughts,,0,0,0,,She speaks less when she's with someone she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:03.42,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But they were always just hanging out together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.28,0:19:19.06,clover,,0,0,0,,Hello? Is this Tairikuken-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:23.06,clover,,0,0,0,,Hey, thanks for waiting! This is Tairikuken!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:25.77,clover,,0,0,0,,Katsudon at 11:30 PM?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.07,0:19:28.42,clover,,0,0,0,,On top of that, they're all extra large?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.32,0:19:32.23,clover,,0,0,0,,This is good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:35.62,clover,,0,0,0,,Oh, Rika-san, it's okay if you can't eat it all. I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:35.95,clover,,0,0,0,,May I have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:37.38,clover,,0,0,0,,Y-Yamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:37.99,clover,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:39.85,clover,,0,0,0,,You're gonna get an upset stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.09,0:19:43.42,clover,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:48.15,clover,,0,0,0,,I mean, I need to get nutrients.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:52.19,clover,,0,0,0,,I need to work hard on my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.49,0:19:54.62,clover,,0,0,0,,And it's getting cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:20:01.93,thoughts,,0,0,0,,So that no matter how precious someone else is to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:07.35,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...I can live strong without being broken in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:15.52,thoughts,,0,0,0,,So that my heart won't be crushed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:20.62,thoughts,,0,0,0,,...even if I see Mayama look worried because of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:24.16,thoughts,,0,0,0,,Is it strange that we don't really talk about anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:29.46,thoughts,,0,0,0,,She speaks less when she's with someone she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:42.70,thoughts,,0,0,0,,But you should go, if that's what you need to do to get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.28,0:20:46.03,thoughts,,0,0,0,,You should go and cry your heart out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.40,0:21:01.36,clover,,0,0,0,,I won't tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:03.93,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm never going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.28,0:21:10.42,clover,,0,0,0,,I'm never going to help push you forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:14.26,clover,,0,0,0,,Figure it out yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.70,0:21:16.94,clover,,0,0,0,,Mayama, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:29.84,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}arifurete iru kimochi nante sa
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.70,0:21:29.84,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,300)}It would be so much easier...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:40.30,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}nanimo iwazu ni isso kieteshimaeba
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.20,0:21:40.30,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...if these stale emotions...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:43.72,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,raku ni nareru no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:43.72,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...could just disappear without a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:52.85,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sorezore no michi wo yuku sono wakaremichi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:52.85,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}At the crossroads where we split ways...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.40,0:22:06.33,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}mou nidoto au koto no nai deai wa kanashisugiru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.40,0:22:06.33,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}...it saddens me to think we may never meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:09.07,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,tarinai kimochi wo mochiyotte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:09.07,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,Despite adding the emotions that are lacking...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:11.93,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,atatameta saki kara hieteitte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:11.93,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,...things cool off just as soon as I warm them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:16.27,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}sonna hazu naitte shinjiteru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.93,0:22:16.27,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}...but I still don't want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:24.97,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}ittai itsumade onaji kotoba wo kakaekondenda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:24.97,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)}Just how long am I going to brood over the same word?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:28.39,cloveredrom,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}kakekondenda
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:28.39,cloveredeng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,300)}How long...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.88,0:22:34.29,clover,,0,0,0,,Next episode: I don't want to see your tears.
